{"word":"H4058 - מָדַד - mâdad - maw-dad' - Measure - அளவு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>מָדַד"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>mâdad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>maw-dad'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Measure / அளவு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அள, அளந்துவிடு, அளக்கப்படு, குப்புறவிழு, அளந்துகொள்ளு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to measure, to stretch"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to measure"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be measured"},{"paragraph":"c) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to extend, to continue"},{"paragraph":"2) to measure, to measure off"},{"paragraph":"d) (Po) measured"},{"paragraph":"e) (Hithpolel) to extend oneself, to stretch oneself"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>stretch</i>; by implication to <i>measure</i> (as if by <i>stretching</i> a line); figuratively to <i>be extended: - </i>measure, mete, stretch self."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4055 - מַד - mad - mad/4055\">H4055</a>, <a href=\"#/H4058 - מָדַד - mâdad - maw-dad'/4058\">H4058</a>, <a href=\"#/H4059 - מִדַּד - middad - mid-dad'/4059\">H4059</a>, <a href=\"#/H4060 - מִדָּה - middâh - mid-daw'/4060\">H4060</a>, <a href=\"#/H4067 - מָדֹון - mâdôwn - maw-dohn'/4067\">H4067</a>, <a href=\"#/H4081 - מִדִּין - Middîyn - mid-deen'/4081\">H4081</a>, <a href=\"#/H4461 - מֵמַד - mêmad - may-mad'/4461\">H4461</a>"}]}